---
title: Easy Miso-Honey Pork & Garlic Rice with Celery Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: Brace your tastebuds because they’re about to be served a huge helping of brilliance in a bowl. Creamy slaw mix against the
earthy miso-honey pork with garlic rice is a spoonful of flavour that will make your mouth water. Sprinkle over some crispy
shallots and brace yourself to be blown away, hang on tight!
